            <h3 class="entry-title">Kolkata Cadences</h3>
        </header>
        <div class="blog-content">
	<p>This summer, me and mom and some of her friends visited Kolkata. We were invited at the residence of Mr. Falguni Ghosh, a writer and a poet. My first day was spent walking around the city footpaths and watching a movie in the film cultural centre, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nandan_(Kolkata)">Nandan</a>, with one of my dear friends from school. Later that day, our party watched a marvellous performance of <em>Sojan Badiar Ghat</em>, a poem written by <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jasimuddin">Jasim Uddin</a>. 
<div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
            <img src="../theatre.jpg" height="400" alt="Theatre Performance">
        </div>
<br><br>

Much of the following day was spent attending <em>Chintak</em>, an annual literature conference organized by Mr. Falguni for the publication of his magazine. There were writers, poets, researchers, and artists giving breif talks, singing and reciting. I myself accompanied a song in harmonium, and also recited one of Falguni's poems.      

<div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
            <img src = "../chintak_1.jpg" alt="Chintak pic 1">
</div>

<br>

The next day, we visited the birthplace of <a href = "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sarada_Devi">Sri Sarada Devi</a>, which is at <a href = "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jayrambati">Jayrambati</a>, under the cruel heat of the summer sun.  
A much needed afternoon nap was then followed by a visit to <a href = "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kamarpukur">Kamarkur</a>, which is the birthplace of <a href = "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramakrishna">Sri Ramakrishna</a>. The evening was spent witnessing an <em>Arati</em>, where a lit lamp was ceremonially waved in front of Ramakrishna's marble statue, and chanting of the Krishna mantras. 

<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 500px)); justify-content: center; gap: 15px; margin: 30px 0;">
